pos_examples: Now, turn satellite object_26 from direction object_50 to direction object_50_67.
[1] (turn_to object_26 object_50_67 object_50) [2] (turn_to o2 o o_67)
Once your done, please take an image of direction object_50 in mode roof_11 using instrument fire on board satellite star_23.
[1] (take_image star_23 object_50 fire roof_11) [2] (take_image o r_11 f b)
First, switch off instrument fire on board satellite star_23 and then calibrate instrument socket for direction object_50_67 using satellite object_26.

[1] (switch_off fire star_23) [2] (switch_off f b)
[1] (calibrate object_26 socket object_50_67) [2] (calibrate z o_67 o2)
The next step is to switch on instrument fire on board satellite star_23.
